DDot.it syntax feature cases, reused as a ddot graph-format test corpus.
Each file isolates one feature of the ddot triple-text syntax: simple triples,
untyped links, inline and multi-line per-link metadata, commands, off/on toggles,
leading-separator continuations, HTML escaping, comma blocks, spaced untyped
links, shorthand commands, and dotted subjects. Originally the ddot.it parser
conformance "cases"; here grouped as "features".

ddot.it/this ..kind.. synthetic
ddot.it/this ..authored by.. Calpano (ddot.it project)
ddot.it/this ..format.. format:ddot
ddot.it/this ..content.. 19 feature cases of the ddot.it triple-text format
ddot.it/this ..tests.. ddot syntax features including inline and multi-line per-link metadata
